Thomas Bruce Akin



Mr. Thomas B. Akin is Independent Director at Mobivity Holdings Corp., Executive Chairman at Dynex Capital, Inc. and Managing General Partner at Talkot Capital LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at eFax.com, Inc. 
Prior to founding Talkot in 1995, Mr. Akin was employed as Chairman by CombiMatrix Corp., a Managing Director by Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc. /Old/, Chairman by Advanced Data Exchange, and Chairman by BrandMuscle, Inc. He also served on the board at Acacia Research Corp. /Old/ and Centiv, Inc. 
Mr. Akin received his undergraduate degree from the University of California, Santa Cruz and an MBA from the University of California, Los Angeles. 



